# Force LF on patch + shell scripts. Without this, Windows git with
# core.autocrlf=true rewrites these files to CRLF on checkout — which
# breaks `git apply` (the patches no longer match LF-line-ended Link
# source) and `sh` invocation (CRLF in shell scripts trips up sh.exe).
*.patch text eol=lf
*.sh    text eol=lf
